        Even though z1 and z2 are the same structure,
        applying set-to-wow!set_to_wow to them yields different results.  With
        z1, altering the carhead also changes the cdrtail, because
        in z1 the carhead and the cdrtail are the same pair.  With
        z2, the carhead and cdrtail are distinct, so set-to-wow! modifies only the carhead:


